&lt;li&gt;Return Body: Returns data of type {Return Type}&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsibility:&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handling HTTP requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Parameter verification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Call application services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Processing response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
