&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend Frameworks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Utilize popular frameworks such as React, Angular, or Vue for building user interfaces that interact with the backend.&lt;/p&gt;
